## 🧠 Overview

AlphaPulse AI is a lightweight crypto intelligence dashboard designed to track market sentiment, identify trending tokens, and generate real-time trading signals.

Built for traders, degens, and alpha hunters.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📊 Live token tracking
- 🤖 AI-powered sentiment scoring
- 🚨 Buy / Watch / Avoid signals
- 📈 Market trend visualization
- 🌙 Clean dark-mode interface

